article_title: Everyone has a crush on Kennedy in her panda onesie [pic] – twitchy.com
article_text:
She looks way better than the Obamacare Pajama Boy.

Gotta watch @kennedynation in a panda onesie Fri 9pm ET on @foxbusiness special #halloween show pic.twitter.com/uSIzeWzvQV — Ed Henry (@edhenryTV) October 28, 2014

@edhenryTV I have such a crush on @kennedynation. — Mollie (@MZHemingway) October 28, 2014

“@MZHemingway: @edhenryTV I have such a crush on @kennedynation.”owwwwwww!!! — Kennedy (@KennedyNation) October 28, 2014

How come Neil Cavuto never dresses like a panda?
